    "description": "A flooded underground water processing facility. The central cistern chamber dominates the map with a large water pool and the only rocket launcher. Two elevated flanking rooms provide sightlines down into the cistern, connected by a dangerous lower maintenance corridor that wraps around with a drop-off shortcut. Risk-reward tension drives every engagement.",
